{"about_the_game":"XII Century: Sir Galgano was confined in prison.<br>After apparition of Saint Michael, he is called upon to eradicating evil that is raging in the soul and human mind subdued by ecclesiastical authority.<br>Struggle against merciless and bloodthirsty enemies in medieval/dark fantasy environments.<br>...have no mercy on them, they won't have any on you...<br><br>Sir Galgano is a side-scrolling medieval beat \u2018em up game with RPG elements.<br>The game places the player in control of the hero.<br>The game drew comparisons to the character The King of Dragons, Rastan Saga, Knights of the Round and Golden Axe.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">KEY FEATURES</h2>The game focuses on the hero, Sir Galgano Guidotti, well-know as Saint Galgano. Player battle the game\u2019s many dangers with weapons and complete quests to acquire experience points, which is used to increase Sir Galgano\u2018s abilities and purchase equipment. <br>Progress is made through the game by slashing your way through enemy\u2019s forces in dynamic environments.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_8_Fatality.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_4_Fatality.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_3_Fatality.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><br>Parry, roll, dodge and attack. <br>He has a variety of weapons, a longsword, a shield and a two-handed sword: there are three modes of attack and many fencing techniques.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_2_Fight.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_6_Fight.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_5_Fight.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><br>Player earn experience points by completing missions. When a player earns enough experience, Sir Galgano\u2019s level increases and the player receives ability points. These points may be used on skill trees and general upgrades have a variety of functions, from raising Sir Galgano\u2019s vitality to improving fencing techniques and activate magic skills.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/2023_03_07_skill_GIF.gif?t=1733608474\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/extras/GIF_7_Magia.gif?t=1733608474\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733608474","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/page.bg.jpg?t=1733608474","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733608474","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1765250/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1733608474","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"demos":[{"appid":2420840,"description":""}],"detailed_description":"<h1>Steam Curator</h1><p><strong>Indie Recommendations</strong><br><i>&quot;Sir Galgano Medieval Tale: Early Preview, Has a solid foundation to build of with a great combat system makes battling the enemies with ease and a focus on adventure adds for an immersive experience.&quot;</i><br><br><br><strong>The Paladin Club</strong><br><i>&quot;SG-AMT (pre alpha review) has a lot of potential! I love the atmosphere of the game, but c